{"tid":2362664,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(G)I-DLE雨琦出道3年第一次剪短髮　曝幕後秘辛：本來要戴假髮的","createTime":"2021-01-11T15:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T19:07:36.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0bf43b671b7e2d47a4925a6b7cb920cd8e5e7098","tid":2362664,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:03:29.000Z","msg":"南韓女團(G)I-DLE（(여자)아이들）發行第四張迷你專輯《I Burn》，這張是由全部由她們作詞作曲的作品，並且由成員小娟擔任製作人。11日的回歸SHOWCASE上，小娟表示這是一張敘述「離別」心情的專輯，造型也引發討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5390/d5390243.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5390%2Fd5390243.jpg&h=5bc97aaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲(G)I-DLE《I Burn》回歸造型融入東方元素。（圖／CUBE娛樂提供）<br />\n<br />\n小娟採用「冬天」、「花朵」和「火花」的意象，詮釋離別到「真正的結束」的故事。成員們穿著帶有東方元素的服裝出席，新聞照釋出後，立刻引爆韓網轟動表示：「太美了！」、「真的是歷代級的概念和美貌。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5390/d5390246.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5390%2Fd5390246.jpg&h=132974cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲(G)I-DLE舒華、穗珍。（圖／CUBE娛樂提供）<br />\n<br />\n這也是成員雨琦出道近3年以來，第一次以短髮造型現身。她在SHOWCASE上表示：「對我來說這是一個很大的挑戰。一開始我是戴著假髮，但看起來像巧克力熊（一個卡通人物）。所以我決定剪掉了，看起來更自然，成員也說很漂亮跟可愛。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5390/d5390242.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5390%2Fd5390242.jpg&h=97637a31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲(G)I-DLE小娟、雨琦。（圖／CUBE娛樂提供）<br />\n<br />\n現場公開最新主打歌《火花》的MV和舞台，舒華爆料：「最後一個鏡頭，小娟姐姐是非常有氣勢的，但拍攝的時候，她不小心笑場了。」這次專輯，泰國成員Minnie的作品也收錄其中，她興奮的說：「能被收在韓文的專輯裡，對我來說是很自豪的事情。我其實一直有持續創作，但要能在專輯裡出現，其實並不容易。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5390/d5390245.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5390%2Fd5390245.jpg&h=9da67328&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5105/d5105831.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5105%2Fd5105831.jpg&h=9e1451da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17d12d798d6f5c057754958ce8c68fa729dbb85f","tid":2362664,"uid":256796,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"長短髮一樣Q<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52db71655d0ce5cb5f6ea629944b049b58da2efe","tid":2362664,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17d12d798d6f5c057754958ce8c68fa729dbb85f","tid":2362664,"uid":256796,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"長短髮一樣Q<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"長短髮一樣Q另有其人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70c601746650f6546f8f3e302e661156916f7cd","tid":2362664,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"52db71655d0ce5cb5f6ea629944b049b58da2efe","tid":2362664,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17d12d798d6f5c057754958ce8c68fa729dbb85f","tid":2362664,"uid":256796,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"長短髮一樣Q<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:06:23.000Z","msg":"長短髮一樣Q另有其人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T15:11:36.000Z","msg":"彩點都比唔上Yqdd..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb9eeaf77563df5eaa32e9cc947799743a9140a","tid":2362664,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e70c601746650f6546f8f3e302e661156916f7cd","tid":2362664,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"52db71655d0ce5cb5f6ea629944b049b58da2efe","tid":2362664,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17d12d798d6f5c057754958ce8c68fa729dbb85f","tid":2362664,"uid":256796,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score"